                <ext:value>description-en:
A smiling child sits on a cushion, holding the Indian national flag in its left hand. A toy rifle is in his right hand, resting on his thigh and other toys - a tank, a plane and a drum can be seem around him.  A partially visible map of India is inscribed on the cushion on which the child sits. (gs/sp)</ext:value>
